&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LEWIS BERRY&lt;/strong&gt; was born on April 27th, 1826 in Gallia Ohio. &lt;!-- UNSOURCED --&gt; Lewis Berry married Eliza Haywood who was also born in Preble County Ohio on November 16, 1833. &lt;!-- UNSOURCED --&gt; Lewis and Eliza were married on March 20th, 1851, Squire Bowen of Thorton, Indiana officiated. Elizabeth Haywood was the daughter of Abijah and Naomi Haywood of Essex County, N.J. Elizabeth&amp;rsquo;s mother died in 1851 and her father Abijah was living with Lewis and Elizabeth in their 1860 and 1870 census listing.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>